Class AbstractSnomedCoreExporter<T extends SnomedDocument>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.exporter.server.AbstractSnomedCoreExporter<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SnomedExporter
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractSnomedRf1CoreExporter, AbstractSnomedRf2CoreExporter, SnomedLanguageRefSetExporter

    public abstract class AbstractSnomedCoreExporter<T extends SnomedDocument>
extends java.lang.Object
implements SnomedExporter
    Base exporter for SNOMED CT concepts, descriptions and relationships. Export is executed based on the requested branchpath where only artefacts visible from the branchpath are exported.
